title: Legitimate Super Bowl Contenders, Did Joe Burrow secure #1 overall pick? (Football 11/13)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Brady Quinn and Ryan Wilson to discuss the 49ers aggressive approach at the end of Monday Night Football (2:30) and which teams are legitimate Super Bowl contenders (13:30). The guys also analyze how the Top 10 of the 2018 Draft would go if teams could pick again (38:30), take a look at Ryan's 2020 NFL Mock Draft (48:30) and answer 5-star questions from Apple Podcasts (1:00:00).
